The '''Republicanists''' were a faction of [[Selonian/Legends|Selonians]] who sought [[Selonia/Legends|Selonia's]] [[planetary repulsor]] as a bargaining chip. They wished to turn it over to the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] in return for a guarantee of Selonia's sovereignty within the New Republic and the [[Corellian sector/Legends|Corellian sector]] government. The [[Hunchuzuc Den]] was a Selonian den affiliated with this group and often fought the [[Absolutists]] in an undeclared Selonian [[Civil war]].

